title: Bug 116564 - The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', now it changes with settings.
OB: When I click on 'OK' and then reopen the hyperlink builder, the actual result is that the title becomes 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected result is that the title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR: To reproduce this issue: 1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'. 2. Open the hyperlink builder. 3. Click on 'OK'. 4. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
